{"tid":832554,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"總有一個人係你既過敏源","createTime":"2018-09-22T22:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T03:59:37.000Z","uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dad8d3d4fe6a1c088b0bd1e0047f7991b3d8342a","tid":832554,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T22:42:22.000Z","msg":"你地相愛過<br />\n<br />\n時間唔長，但背叛收場<br />\n<br />\n剛完既年頭<br />\n<br />\n男既覺得女既勾三搭四，不要也罷<br />\n<br />\n但三年過去，卻未能忘卻<br />\n<br />\n是不捨？不甘？<br />\n<br />\n男心想：若當年冇太絕，今日仲會有朋友關係？<br />\n<br />\n不！！<br />\n<br />\n咁就眼見佢同人眉來眼去再若無其事地同你曖味？<br />\n<br />\n你深知，你唔會再信佢<br />\n<br />\n但你亦知， 你一直都愛佢<br />\n<br />\n就好似你對蝦敏感一樣<br />\n<br />\n你可以選擇唔食蝦，但唔食唔代表過敏消失了<br />\n<br />\n所以離開對大家都係好最既選擇<br />\n<br />\n就好似對蝦敏感既人唔食蝦一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹有感而發叫下春<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 199999"},{"pid":"b2a5cb0d9c9c4d2ab8c2d5e739595a1bd68a4a7c","tid":832554,"uid":13207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T23:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/lo